      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776942364,
      "updated": 1776943045
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9fd26000000000018d459",
      "text": " 2. https://prado-therapy.com/childish-omnipotence/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776942375,
      "updated": 1776943046
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9fd2b000000000018d45a",
      "text": " 3. https://harada-mentalcl.com/blog/幼児的万能感",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1776942379,
      "updated": 1776943047
    },
    {
      "id": "69e9fd2e000000000018d45b",
      "text": " 4. https://oyako-heart.com/mental-problem/厄介な幼児的万能感/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
